  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4c24e01ed0a48f14a8ec8de924835528, type: 3}
  m_Name: Page3ARTIST
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  thoughts:
  - E.S. The initials appear on an old label, almost worn away. No one calls him by name. They call him the Unsigned Artist, as if his identity no longer matters.
  - I found one of his works among the old books. The colors have not dried, even after all these years. I touched the canvas. It was warm.
  - Sometimes I think he did not disappear. He just thinned out into his work. He is looking back at me from inside it, waiting for me to find him.
  tasks: []
  collectibles: []
